The remaining problem is that proxy_lb_workers() only gives a good value when
the config file has been parsed (can't be used in preconfig().

author: rickhall
msg: The _resolveBundle() method was mistakenly setting the bundle's state to
RESOLVED, which was causing problems if the bundle was already active when
resolve was called. The RESOLVED state is automatically set as a result
of a RESOLVED event from the resolver and does not need to be set here.
